data.description: Welcome to your dream townhouse in a prime location of Bonita! This meticulously maintained original owner property offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Situated steps away from the vibrant town center with a restaurant, pools, and post office, this townhouse boasts an unparalleled location. This home is the epitome of elegance and functionality. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting living area that exudes a model home feel. 1st floor bedroom is perfect for guests or a home office, complete with its own private porch. Venturing upstairs, you'll discover two ensuite bedrooms, each offering its own private bathroom for maximum convenience and privacy. The master bedroom further spoils you with a balcony. Throughout the home, you'll find exquisite tile and wood floors, adding a touch of luxury to your living space. Village Walk of Bonita offers an array of resort-style amenities to enhance your lifestyle. Enjoy lazy days by the pristine resort-style pool, stay active with a lap pool and a fitness center, or engage in friendly competition with neighbors on the 8 clay tennis courts. Don't miss this incredible opportunity.
